

IMAGE SEQUENCE > VIDEO
=============================================


sudo gst-launch multifilesrc location=grab_%05d.png caps="image/png, framerate=10/1" ! pngdec ! ffmpegcolorspace ! jpegenc ! avimux ! filesink location=video.avi sync=false


switcher -d &
switcher-ctrl -C uridecodebin video
switcher-ctrl -s video loop true
switcher-ctrl -i video to_shmdata 'path/to/the/file'





